---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const seo = { title: 'Terms of Service — BrandsBuilders', description: 'Terms governing services provided by BrandsBuilders.', canonical: 'https://brandsbuilders.ca/terms-of-service' };
---
<Layout seo={seo}>
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: 2026-01-13</p>
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>BrandsBuilders provides revenue efficiency systems including missed-call protection, show-up optimization, and client reactivation services.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Services</h2>
      <p>Services are delivered as described in a written proposal or SOW. Scope, timelines, and dependencies are defined per engagement.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Fees</h2>
      <p>$1,000/month. Month-to-month. Invoices payable according to stated terms.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Revenue Recovery Guarantee</h2>
      <p>5 recovered leads booked in your calendar within 30 days of going live — or your money back. Guarantee applies when agreed execution conditions are met.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Alberta and Canadian federal law.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>BrandsBuilders · Alberta, Canada · <a href="mailto:hello@brandsbuilders.ca" class="text-orange-600">hello@brandsbuilders.ca</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>